     "text": [
      "笨・feature_analysis.json 菫晏ｭ伜ｮ御ｺ・ (45.1 KB)\n",
      "  迚ｹ蠕ｴ驥・ 105 蛻・ |  鬮倡嶌髢｢繝壹い: 30  |  ROI: {'n_races': 24431, 'top1_win_rate': 0.3256, 'top1_show_rate': 0.9264, 'top3_hit_rate': 0.5754, 'roi_top1_pct': 63.99, 'avg_implied_prob': 0.1854}\n"
